org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM users INNER JOIN groups_users ON users.id = groups_users.group_id WHERE users.type IN ('Group', 'GroupBuiltin', 'GroupAnonymous', 'GroupNonMember') AND groups_users.user_id = "$1" AND users.id = "$2" LIMIT "$3"

rewrites.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM users WHERE users.type IN ('Group', 'GroupBuiltin', 'GroupAnonymous', 'GroupNonMember') AND users.id = "$2" LIMIT "$3"
